        "content": "<p>I can't find any contradiction in <a href=\"https://docs.julialang.org/en/v1/manual/variables/#Allowed-Variable-Names\">Julia - Allowed Variable Names</a></p>\n<p><code>\\ttzero =  U+1D7F6</code></p>",
